      "factId": "hz.web.6a53e3b2f5b03b87.fact.3",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "In Sinatra, for example, a callback might look something like this: # Support both GET and POST for callbacks %w(get post).each do |method| send(method, &ldquo;/auth/:provider/callback&rdquo;) do env[&lsquo;omniauth.auth&rsquo;] # =&gt; OmniAuth::AuthHash end end For additional documentation, you should see the OmniAuth wiki.",
